{"tid":1542071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家可唔可以幫下我","createTime":"2019-09-04T17:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T18:33:22.000Z","uid":199636,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"548dfa56aaa40bde7ca8b1573b59b644989b9591","tid":1542071,"uid":199636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:44:37.000Z","msg":"身邊嘅朋友都繼續返學，繼續搭車俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我又罷課又跳閘，搞到我好似個廢青咁<br />\n大家可唔可以幫幫手...話俾我知我做緊嘅野係為咗香港，係有意義嘅<br />\n最緊要可唔可以陪我一齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b8b0676de7cfab696b5c865ce5956285f261fc","tid":1542071,"uid":199636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:44:51.000Z","msg":"係咪我係廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9635cf8eaf6f00f1418fd015ee3105147305e1b5","tid":1542071,"uid":127333,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:46:07.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 你啲同學朋友先係廢青<br />\n依家係眾人皆醉你獨醒呀"},{"pid":"4245e5e2d788d65aaa697956fc7a7045a2a84a4e","tid":1542071,"uid":30756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:46:25.000Z","msg":"咁有意義都話廢<br />\n你為香港未來付出緊㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65529d45bece03f053bdc410fbe30159ebee39a0","tid":1542071,"uid":35426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:47:04.000Z","msg":"只係你走得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油啊手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130668de763c62ac0338d2c4dba4524b5627077a","tid":1542071,"uid":199636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:47:23.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以一齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64188b6dd942ea002995e12677b57ba4cf1b1c3d","tid":1542071,"uid":301929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:48:09.000Z","msg":"NO <br />\n你好勇敢<br />\n每個人睇法唔到 要面對的都唔同<br />\n可能其他人未必有勇氣去到敢盡<br />\n如果你都有一點倦 可以先休息一下<br />\n再出 再想方法"},{"pid":"1fc36bc1e8710190e9544edf6874dc9c4d55785b","tid":1542071,"uid":67632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:48:11.000Z","msg":"可能呢一刻你覺得無意義，但係你所做嘅嘢係為咗將來，千祈唔好諗埋一邊，你仲有好多戰友㗎"},{"pid":"578812d58238f638c9ee948bde6f751b37b0ece9","tid":1542071,"uid":30955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:48:36.000Z","msg":"一啲都唔廢 最有用就係你！<br />\n我啲同學話好期待睇我跳閘<br />\n點知原來只係當睇馬騮戲 繼續拍卡<br />\n我都好失望 唯有繼續感染佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1088930019fdcc370c094533c920a36d7bc3ffad","tid":1542071,"uid":199636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:48:40.000Z","msg":"點解你地繼續返學啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都有tutorial有reg到外語堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b439032d6fcae3d0ccc8983cf6971b5fa453616","tid":1542071,"uid":199636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"578812d58238f638c9ee948bde6f751b37b0ece9","tid":1542071,"uid":30955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:48:36.000Z","msg":"一啲都唔廢 最有用就係你！<br />\n我啲同學話好期待睇我跳閘<br />\n點知原來只係當睇馬騮戲 繼續拍卡<br />\n我都好失望 唯有繼續感染佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:49:21.000Z","msg":"我都以為可以感染到佢地 已經喺佢地面前跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d87035e13c72213d8b9ed1ec9b9fe1b1c528d6","tid":1542071,"uid":199636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:49:54.000Z","msg":"多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但可唔可以推到俾更加多大學生睇"},{"pid":"2f7ad9352030bde1a16728a477f85aa108f43d30","tid":1542071,"uid":30756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"130668de763c62ac0338d2c4dba4524b5627077a","tid":1542071,"uid":199636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:47:23.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以一齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:50:02.000Z","msg":"我已經罷咗六年工喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2649af298e251b844f43ded444c1f414f38aa035","tid":1542071,"uid":280926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:50:19.000Z","msg":"你好叻仔！堅持做你覺得正確嘅事！"},{"pid":"91bcb4aeb3b1ebdb0c92a464c41242c1baa8794e","tid":1542071,"uid":199636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:50:44.000Z","msg":"點解第一個星期就已經唔敢霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解跳閘咁簡單都唔去做下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8c36670957325f182b8d9be48da290970597db","tid":1542071,"uid":199636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:52:20.000Z","msg":"添馬好大咩 點解前日出黎都係未坐滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad84fa54eef99fb3f12a0719d06658a178f703a","tid":1542071,"uid":217281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:52:41.000Z","msg":"香港需要好似你咁勇敢既年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油呀！"},{"pid":"67c3e5f877a3c6fbd055794c160157766d330e18","tid":1542071,"uid":290968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:52:45.000Z","msg":"只要你老左同你個孫講, 當年發生左件咁既事, 而你又係依件事當中參與到咩程度,咩行為, 講完之後都無悔, 已經足夠"},{"pid":"a687d2903270b79063a61bf9ae0d3356b93f3112","tid":1542071,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:54:02.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n<br />\n分別在於:<br />\n3隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n8人離世<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC3deC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC3deC.jpg&h=34367fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2LPVhj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2LPVhj.jpg&h=35c3dac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4TBAhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4TBAhk.jpg&h=05bdd3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8LoZ1q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8LoZ1q.jpg&h=fac47d55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a6dd88f0396952f4c763b5542415bfed950def1","tid":1542071,"uid":19501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:54:11.000Z","msg":"覺得啱就做，我平時都好少見人跳閘<br />\n但我都照跳咗成個星期，仲會一直繼續跳，畀其他人見到我嘅行動<br />\n一個人嘅力量微細，但只要鼓勵到多一個人跳，我都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098344c8b9bfca1fef557e6351b098ba307090ee","tid":1542071,"uid":199636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:54:29.000Z","msg":"朋友們，我已經唔會要求你同我一齊企到上前線，但係依啲野好簡單姐，唔好令我對你地失望啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3725e62e4777305406b63f8f5a4c04bc4d84b8","tid":1542071,"uid":9570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi